14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 68 O.S. 2021, Section 2890, as
16 amended by Section 1, Chapter 5, 1st Extraordinary Session, O.S.L.
17 2023 (68 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 2890), is amended to read as
18 follows:
19 Section 2890. A. In addition to the amount of the homestead
20 exemption authorized and allowed in Section 2889 of this title, an
21 additional exemption is hereby granted, to the extent of One
22 Thousand Dollars ($1,000.00) of the assessed valuation on each
23 homestead of heads of households whose gross household income from
24
